# NSScroller.KnobStyle.default

**Case**

Specifies a dark knob with a light border.

## Declaration

```swift
case `default`
```

## Discussion

This is the default style; it is good against any background.

## Constants

- **NSScroller.KnobStyle.dark**: Specifies a dark knob.
- **NSScroller.KnobStyle.light**: Specifies a light knob.
